kpi_info.title: Nr of CPICH RSCP acceptable values on RRC conn req
kpi_info.use: The number of CPICH RSCP values reported by the UEs in which the value is -101 dBm <= CPICH RSCP < -74 dBm, when the RNC receives RRC: RRC CONNECTION REQUEST from the UE.
